fields.name: breadcrumb
fields.title: Breadcrumb
fields.description: A set of links that can help a user understand and navigate a website hierarchy.

fields.name: lastReviewed
fields.title: Last Reviewed
fields.description: Date on which the content on this web page was last reviewed for accuracy and/or completeness.

fields.name: mainContentOfPage
fields.title: Main Content of Page
fields.description: Indicates if this web page element is the main subject of the page.

fields.name: primaryImageOfPage
fields.title: Primary Image of Page
fields.description: Indicates the main image on the page

fields.name: relatedLink
fields.title: Related Link
fields.description: A link related to this web page, for example to other related web pages.

fields.name: reviewedBy
fields.title: Reviewed by
fields.description: People or organizations that have reviewed the content on this web page for accuracy and/or completeness.
